{"title":"Bestow Arms","url":"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/Bestow_Arms","type":"markdown","data":"***Version [0.32](/0.32 \"0.32\")**: This article is up to date for the [latest stable release](/0.32 \"0.32\") of *Dungeon Crawl Stone Soup*.*\n\n|   |                                                                                                                                             |\n| - | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n|   | Temporarily grants numerous nearby allies a magical weapon from within the armoury, so long as the souls holding it together remain intact. |\n\n**Bestow Arms** is a monster-only spell that temporarily grants copies of a random summoned weapon to 5-7 nearby allies. These tend to be top-tier items, with good [brands](/Brand \"Brand\") and [enchantment](/Enchantment \"Enchantment\") (from +4 to +9), with a slight bias towards polearms, but also including launchers.\n\nPossible weapons:\n\n- [bardiche](/Bardiche \"Bardiche\")\n- [glaive](/Glaive \"Glaive\")\n- [demon trident](/Demon_trident \"Demon trident\")\n- [eveningstar](/Eveningstar \"Eveningstar\")\n- [double sword](/Double_sword \"Double sword\")\n- [quick blade](/Quick_blade \"Quick blade\")\n- [longbow](/Longbow \"Longbow\")\n- [triple crossbow](/Triple_crossbow \"Triple crossbow\")\n- [hand cannon](/Hand_cannon \"Hand cannon\")\n\nThese weapons will be branded with either [flame](/Flame \"Flame\"), [freezing](/Freezing \"Freezing\"), [speed](/Speed_\\(brand\\) \"Speed (brand)\"), [vampiric](/Vampiric \"Vampiric\"), [chaos](/Chaos \"Chaos\"), or [distortion](/Distortion \"Distortion\"). Note that even ranged weapons can get any brand from this list, including vampiric or distortion, which normally don't appear on such weapons.\n\nThe following enemies cast Bestow Arms:\n\n- v [![Undying armoury.png](/images/0/0f/Undying_armoury.png)](/File:Undying_armoury.png) **[Undying armoury](/Undying_armoury \"Undying armoury\")**\n\n## Tips & Tricks\n\nWorshippers of [Yred](/Yred \"Yred\") have a special use for this spell. If you manage to bind soul of a monster that wields a weapon created by Bestow Arms, the weapon will become permanent. A bound [yaktaur captain](/Yaktaur_captain \"Yaktaur captain\") with a triple crossbow of distortion can be an amazing ally!\n\n## History\n\n- This spell was added in [0.32](/0.32 \"0.32\").\n","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html class=\"client-nojs\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\"/>\n<title>Bestow Arms - CrawlWiki</title>\n<script>document.documentElement.className = document.documentElement.className.replace( /(^|\\s)client-nojs(\\s|$)/, \"$1client-js$2\" );</script>\n<script>(window.RLQ=window.RLQ||[]).push(function(){mw.config.set({\"wgCanonicalNamespace\":\"\",\"wgCanonicalSpecialPageName\":false,\"wgNamespaceNumber\":0,\"wgPageName\":\"Bestow_Arms\",\"wgTitle\":\"Bestow Arms\",\"wgCurRevisionId\":81056,\"wgRevisionId\":81056,\"wgArticleId\":11576,\"wgIsArticle\":true,\"wgIsRedirect\":false,\"wgAction\":\"view\",\"wgUserName\":null,\"wgUserGroups\":[\"*\"],\"wgCategories\":[\"0.32 articles\",\"Monster spells\"],\"wgBreakFrames\":false,\"wgPageContentLanguage\":\"en\",\"wgPageContentModel\":\"wikitext\",\"wgSeparatorTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDigitTransformTable\":[\"\",\"\"],\"wgDefaultDateFormat\":\"dmy\",\"wgMonthNames\":[\"\",\"January\",\"February\",\"March\",\"April\",\"May\",\"June\",\"July\",\"August\",\"September\",\"October\",\"November\",\"December\"],\"wgMonthNamesShort\":[\"\",\"Jan\",\"Feb\",\"Mar\",\"Apr\",\"May\",\"Jun\",\"Jul\",\"Aug\",\"Sep\",\"Oct\",\"Nov\",\"Dec\"],\"wgRelevantPageName\":\"Bestow_Arms\",\"wgRelevantArticleId\":11576,\"wgRequestId\":\"87fb6786cd96efd37766dde3\",\"wgIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRelevantPageIsProbablyEditable\":false,\"wgRestrictionEdit\":[],\"wgRestrictionMove\":[]});mw.loader.state({\"site.styles\":\"ready\",\"noscript\"