en)\"/>\n<link rel=\"EditURI\" type=\"application/rsd+xml\" href=\"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/api.php?action=rsd\"/>\n<!--[if lt IE 9]><script src=\"/resources/lib/html5shiv/html5shiv.min.js?40bd4\"></script><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Bestow_Arms rootpage-Bestow_Arms skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\t\twindow.google_analytics_uacct = \"UA-3380984-8\";\n</script>\n<div class=\"adsense\">\n\t\t<script type=\"text/javascript\"><!--\n\t\tgoogle_ad_client = \"ca-pub-7088061744296615\";\n\t\t/* CrawlWiki skyscraper */\n\t\tgoogle_ad_slot = \"8196155564\";\n\t\tgoogle_ad_width = 160;\n\t\tgoogle_ad_height = 600;\n-->\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\"\nsrc=\"http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js\">\n</script>\n</div>\n\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n\t\t\t<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Bestow Arms</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From CrawlWiki</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\">\n\t\t\t\t\tJump to:\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#mw-head\">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #33FF66; background-color: #99FF99; border-left: 15px solid #33FF66; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Version <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">0.32</a></b>: This article is up to date for the <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">latest stable release</a> of </i>Dungeon Crawl Stone Soup<i>.</div></i>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> Temporarily grants numerous nearby allies a magical weapon from within the armoury, so long as the souls holding it together remain intact.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><b>Bestow Arms</b> is a monster-only spell that temporarily grants copies of a random summoned weapon to 5-7 nearby allies. These tend to be top-tier items, with good <a href=\"/Brand\" title=\"Brand\">brands</a> and <a href=\"/Enchantment\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Enchantment\">enchantment</a> (from +4 to +9), with a slight bias towards polearms, but also including launchers.\n</p><p>Possible weapons:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Bardiche\" title=\"Bardiche\">bardiche</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Glaive\" title=\"Glaive\">glaive</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Demon_trident\" title=\"Demon trident\">demon trident</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Eveningstar\" title=\"Eveningstar\">eveningstar</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Double_sword\" title=\"Double sword\">double sword</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Quick_blade\" title=\"Quick blade\">quick blade</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Longbow\" title=\"Longbow\">longbow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Triple_crossbow\" title=\"Triple crossbow\">triple crossbow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/Hand_cannon\" title=\"Hand cannon\">hand cannon</a></li></ul>\n<p>These weapons will be branded with either <a href=\"/Flame\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Flame\">flame</a>, <a href=\"/Freezing\" title=\"Freezing\">freezing</a>, <a href=\"/Speed_(brand)\" title=\"Speed (brand)\">speed</a>, <a href=\"/Vampiric\" title=\"Vampiric\">vampiric</a>, <a href=\"/Chaos\" title=\"Chaos\">chaos</a>, or <a href=\"/Distortion\" title=\"Distortion\">distortion</a>. Note that even ranged weapons can get any brand from this list, including vampiric or distortion, which normally don't appear on such weapons.\n</p><p>The following enemies cast Bestow Arms:\n</p>\n<ul><li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-brightmagenta\">v</span> <a href=\"/File:Undying_armoury.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Undying armoury.png\" src=\"/images/0/0f/Undying_armoury.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Undying_armoury\" title=\"Undying armoury\">Undying armoury</a></b></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tips_.26_Tricks\">Tips &amp; Tricks</span></h2>\n<p>Worshippers of <a href=\"/Yred\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Yred\">Yred</a> have a special use for this spell. If you manage to bind soul of a monster that wields a weapon created by Bestow Arms, the weapon will become permanent. A bound <a href=\"/Yaktaur_captain\" title=\"Yaktaur captain\">yaktaur captain</a> with a triple crossbow of distortion can be an amazing ally!\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>This spell was added in <a href=\"/0.32\" title=\"0.32\">0.32</a>.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916043114\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.068 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.200 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 46/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 207/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1756/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 203/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 4/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nLua time usage: 0.060s\nLua virtual size: 13.75 MB / 50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  175.219      1 -total\n 79.66%  139.573      1 Template:Monsters_with_spell\n 19.42%   34.036      1 Template:Version032\n 18.62%   32.618      1 Template:Version\n 11.39%   19.959      1 Template:Glyph\n  0.71%    1.247      1 Template:Flavour\n-->\n</d